"""Start the Python interpreter and use it as calculator.

1. How many seconds are there in 42 minutes 42 seconds?
2. How many miles are there in 10 kilometers? Hint: there are 1.61 kilometers in a mile.
3. If you run a 10 kilometer race in 42 minutes 42 seconds, what is your average pace (time per mile in minutes and seconds)?
   What is your average speed in miles per hour?"""

#1
42 * 60 + 42 #2562 seconds in 42 minutes 42 seconds

#2
10 / 1.61 #6.2 miles in 10 kilometers

#3
2562 / 6.2 #413 seconds per mile
413 / 60 #6.8 minutes per miles
60 * 0.8 #48 | 6 minutes and 48 seconds per miles

60 * 60 #3600 seconds in hour
3600 / 413 #8.7 miles per hour